title: Marriage Struggles & Your Birth-Order
itunes:author: Guests: Dr. Kevin Leman
itunes:summary:
Whether you're a first-born or the baby of the family, we all have a common struggle—selfishness. How do you get rid of it? John and the Smalley's talk about learning to recognize and let go of selfishness in their own marriages. Featuring Dr. Kevin Leman.

Find us online at focusonthefamily.com/marriagepodcast or call 1-800-A-FAMILY

The Birth Order Book: https://store.focusonthefamily.com/singleitem/checkout/donation/item/don-fofm-podcast-2020-07-28#refcd=982401
